      <Property Name="Location">3, 65</Property>
      <Property Name="Text">This demo simulates a Fuel Control Management System (FCMS). In Simulated Mode the FCMS is stimulated by an 
external FDX-Program that operates on the Overhead Fuel Panel on FCMS Panels desktop. The Fuel Computer shows 
the actual Pump status of the FCMS. 
For more Information, please press the [Help] button.</Property>
